data.description: This home is a corner lot with 5 spacious bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms and 2 half bathrooms with a three car garage located in the highly regarded gated community of East Lake Park. Also features a private screened in saltwater pool and plenty of space in the back veranda. The first floor consists of bamboo flooring throughout with tile in the custom kitchen. The home also comes with a first-floor master suite with his and hers accommodations. The second floor features a huge bonus room and spacious loft with carpet throughout. The East Lake community is family friendly with parks and great schools in the area. The home is in a great location with being only minutes from Lake Nona Medical City, and the Orlando International Airport and many more.
